      "author": "Hobeom",
      "description": "## Mouse Navigation v1.1.0\r\n\r\nThis release introduces a safer upgrade path for the new gesture system.\r\n\r\n### Highlights\r\n- Added a **Gesture Engine** setting with two options:\r\n  - `modern-v2`\r\n  - `legacy-v1`\r\n- Existing users upgrading from older versions default to **legacy-v1** to preserve behavior.\r\n- New installs default to **modern-v2**.\r\n- Added language support updates for the new setting (English/Korean).\r\n- Included TypeScript and command API compatibility fixes for improved build stability.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\nIf you notice behavior differences after upgrading, open plugin settings and switch the Gesture Engine to **legacy-v1**.",
